     Created: 2026-03-06
     Description:
         Color token definitions for the Light (default) theme. Defines all Dock*
         and Panel_* resource keys consumed by Light/ control templates and
         PanelCommon.xaml. Also includes TabColorizer styles for the light tab strip.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. First merged dictionary in Generic.xaml, MinimalTheme.xaml,
         and OfficeTheme.xaml (via their respective Colors.xaml). Serves as the
         canonical light palette reference for the docking system.
     ========================================================== -->

